1
00:00:29,530 --> 00:00:30,800
Yao'er has been missing for over a decade.

2
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:32,930
I finally sensed her life token again.

3
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:35,200
Which lower realm is she in now?

4
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:38,030
My poor daughter.

5
00:00:38,030 --> 00:00:39,160
Missing for so long,

6
00:00:39,330 --> 00:00:40,600
she must have suffered countless hardships.

7
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:42,160
Our dignified Longevity Immortal Clan

8
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:43,000
actually raised her in poverty.

9
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:44,300
Wandering outside for so many years,

10
00:00:44,300 --> 00:00:45,300
we truly let her down.

11
00:00:45,300 --> 00:00:46,200
After finding her,

12
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:47,430
we must use all the resources of our immortal clan

13
00:00:47,430 --> 00:00:49,030
to properly make it up to her.

14
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,230
Father, Mother.

15
00:00:54,530 --> 00:00:55,800
Back when the clan was in chaos,

16
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:57,600
Wanyi risked her life to flee with Third Sister.

17
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:59,030
Now we finally have a clue.

18
00:00:59,030 --> 00:01:01,130
I am willing to personally go through the Ancient Reception Hall

19
00:01:01,130 --> 00:01:02,760
to the lower realm to find Third Sister.

20
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:05,000
I will never let her suffer any more grievances.

21
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,560
Descending from the Immortal Realm

22
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:08,730
will inevitably be suppressed by the will of the lower realm's heaven and earth.

23
00:01:08,730 --> 00:01:10,160
Even if you are a True Immortal,

24
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:13,430
you can at most exert the strength of a peak Quasi-Emperor after descending.

25
00:01:13,430 --> 00:01:14,900
I fear there might be unexpected dangers.

26
00:01:14,900 --> 00:01:16,200
If you encounter a life-and-death crisis,

27
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,330
crush this talisman

28
00:01:17,330 --> 00:01:18,700
to ask the clan for help.

29
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,000
Yes, Father.

30
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:28,800
I...

31
00:01:29,300 --> 00:01:30,360
I'm not dead.

32
00:01:30,900 --> 00:01:33,430
I, Ji Qingchen, have been reborn!

33
00:01:37,530 --> 00:01:38,500
In my past life,

34
00:01:38,729 --> 00:01:42,160
as the youngest Deity Transformation cultivator of the Taixuan Holy Land,

35
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,420
I treated Su Yao as my own flesh and blood.

36
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:47,460
Yet she used her innocence to slander me, a Deity Transformation cultivator,

37
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:50,300
saying I stole her lousy Foundation Establishment pills.

38
00:01:50,300 --> 00:01:51,100
Hmph.

39
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,020
What's ridiculous is that

40
00:02:04,530 --> 00:02:06,160
no matter how I explained,

41
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:10,560
all I got was my master's distance and my fellow disciples' disdain.

42
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,430
I guarded the Heavenly Abyss for the sect,

43
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:19,360
defending against the Demon Race.

44
00:02:21,100 --> 00:02:22,960
I narrowly escaped death countless times,

45
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:25,060
but in the end, no one believed me.

46
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:27,360
Causing me to freeze to death on a street corner,

47
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,760
without even a straw mat to wrap my corpse.

48
00:02:32,900 --> 00:02:34,160
Calculating the time,

49
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,430
it's almost time for junior sister Su Yao

50
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:37,090
to join the Taixuan Holy Land.

51
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,890
That treatment like the darling of the world,

52
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:41,329
the master's favoritism,

53
00:02:41,329 --> 00:02:44,190
and the flattery of the senior and junior brothers.

54
00:02:48,130 --> 00:02:51,430
Since you all abandoned me in this Taixuan Holy Land,

55
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:52,760
I might as well not stay.

56
00:02:53,300 --> 00:02:54,500
I, Ji Qingchen,

57
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:56,020
will leave the sect today!

58
00:03:01,460 --> 00:03:04,330
Holy Lord, heaven blesses our Taixuan!

59
00:03:05,730 --> 00:03:09,060
This is the Flying Immortal Physique, rare in all eternity!

60
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:16,360
What pure bloodline power.

61
00:03:27,230 --> 00:03:28,160
Hahaha!

62
00:03:28,460 --> 00:03:30,060
Heaven blesses our Taixuan!

63
00:03:30,860 --> 00:03:33,790
The Flying Immortal Physique, rare in all eternity!

64
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:34,900
Little girl,

65
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:38,560
are you willing to be my personal closed-door disciple?

66
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,900
I am willing to use all the foundation of the Holy Land

67
00:03:40,900 --> 00:03:42,660
to protect you until you achieve the Dao.

68
00:03:42,660 --> 00:03:45,560
Gu Linyuan, the humiliation you gave me,

69
00:03:45,730 --> 00:03:49,329
I will certainly repay you thousands of times over in the future.

70
00:03:50,829 --> 00:03:52,100
Disciple Su Yao

71
00:03:52,100 --> 00:03:52,930
pays respects to Master.

72
00:03:52,930 --> 00:03:53,760
Master, wait.

73
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:05,260
Qingchen, why aren't you guarding the Heavenly Abyss?

74
00:04:05,260 --> 00:04:06,590
What are you doing here?

75
00:04:06,830 --> 00:04:08,690
Come and meet your junior sister.

76
00:04:08,930 --> 00:04:10,700
She possesses the Flying Immortal Physique

77
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:14,660
and shoulders the responsibility of the future revival of our Taixuan Holy Land.

78
00:04:14,660 --> 00:04:16,060
There is no need, Master.

79
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:17,690
I am here to leave the sect.

80
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:19,360
Nonsense!

81
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:23,260
You are the Saintess of our Taixuan Holy Land,

82
00:04:23,260 --> 00:04:25,660
bearing the responsibility of guarding Tianyuan.

83
00:04:25,660 --> 00:04:27,430
How can you easily leave the sect?

84
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:29,060
Why do I feel that the Taixuan Saintess

85
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,960
has an inexplicable hostility towards me?

86
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,620
I haven't offended her at all.

87
00:04:32,730 --> 00:04:35,659
Could she be jealous of my Flying Immortal Physique,

88
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:37,230
worrying that once I arrive,

89
00:04:37,230 --> 00:04:39,730
I will steal her spotlight and glory?

90
00:04:42,730 --> 00:04:44,260
Reporting to the Holy Lord.

91
00:04:44,460 --> 00:04:46,659
Gu Linyuan, the head of the Gu family, has come to visit.
